item.title: Changing server name (rsps)?
item.dc:creator: @karilz0 karilz0
item.description:
@karilz0 wrote:

[quote=“gangsta57, post:2, topic:409691”]Uhm server name ?,

First go to , client.java (server sided) and search for the current server name and change to yours. Search also for ówner. If you find it change the name to your username.

If you want to change client name : Go to client.java change there the names to yours. and RSframe in client side.

P.S : YOU CAN SEARCH EASY WITH DOING CRTL+F

thanks but idk if it works… lol anyway thanks =) ily (no gay) lol ;)[/quote]
